{"tid":1661840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰缐] 歐洲巡迴展覧第三站","createTime":"2019-10-18T11:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T18:36:03.000Z","uid":73212,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db14a3974b9a503bd88507d371fce7b1c0d437d3","tid":1661840,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Free Hong Kong Exhibition團隊</span></span><br />\n第一站 : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1592876/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1592876/page/1</a><br />\n第二站 : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1642644/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1642644/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\n又係我地呀，响呢個月𥚃面我地已經黎到第三站柏林，响德國首都繼續宣揚港共嘅所作所為，令更多外國人關注香港。<br />\n<br />\n完成呢次展覽之後，我地已經同其他城市聯絡，繼續籌備下一個展覧，希望繼續接觸更多外國人，令更多人留意香港。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Facebook專頁</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Free-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFree-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=c5296571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Free-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239/</a><br />\n<br />\nFree Hong Kong Exhibition團隊由一班海外香港人組成，希望以巡迴展覧形式，將香港人嘅聲音帶到海外。作為响城牆外生活嘅人，我地自覺有責任將港共政府嘅所作所為話俾全世界知。我地或者無能力直接接觸各國政要，但係响西方民主社會，人民就係力量，展覽正正就可以提供一個空間及平台直接與一般市民接觸交流。<br />\n<br />\n我地團隊可以做嘅並唔多，希望大家一齊努力，遍地開花。香港人加油！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"2b555065ffaa6ce5e33308e76483e6d14587d43f","tid":1661840,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ae50ce52f3851b9fb3d9bb0cfd82bb01a8be04","tid":1661840,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re