Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=32a2fe6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你入    /task2</span></span><br />\n就可以搵到以上的新聞<br />\n<br />\nRetweet 加 cm ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得每日做！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你入 /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就可以見到人權法新聞同議員的tweet<br />\n<br />\n記得多謝埋人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9ca49b5662dcad576baaace27f6c25498cd08d","tid":1661840,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"18cf815252f21175a3bacc2de568f57bac03bbbb","tid":1661840,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:38:31.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"54a79c13f4e3b51673af80fcb3a154bd009309d5","tid":1661840,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc5a014b33aef935646653481e9a35fc2ab0ba2c","tid":1661840,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:40:37.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5407e23c27e2b5fbbe51a17df68092d197831f7b","tid":1661840,"uid":299227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"多謝哂咁多位海外巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6301975231ebe115bd398ba6a281f7423663030","tid":1661840,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"071c02362b12aa6e2268c798c62b209795e0f462","tid":1661840,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"7a12a88cd6c0be2a382158978ac0ad